OTHER INFORMATION FILED BY THE COMPANY WITH THE SEC ARE AVAILABLE ON THE COMPANY'S WEBSITE AT HTTP://WWW.APPLE.COM/INVESTOR WHEN SUCH REPORTS ARE AVAILABLE ON THE SEC WEBSITE. THE PUBLIC MAY READ AND

