APPLE COMPUTER, INC.

, WAS FILED IN ONTARIO, CANADA ON JANUARY 9, 2006 SEEKING AUTHORIZATION TO INSTITUTE A CLASS ACTION ON BEHALF OF IPOD NANO PURCHASERS IN

CANADA. APPLE CANADA INC. AND APPLE COMPUTER, INC. HAVE SERVED NOTICES OF INTENT TO DEFEND.

