DIVISION, ALLEGING INFRINGEMENT OF U.S. PATENT NO. 7,065,417 ENTITLED "MPEG PORTABLE SOUND REPRODUCING SYSTEM AND A REPRODUCING METHOD THEREOF." THE COMPLAINT SEEKS UNSPECIFIED DAMAGES AND

