(1)

AUDIT

FEES RELATE TO PROFESSIONAL SERVICES RENDERED IN CONNECTION WITH THE AUDIT OF THE COMPANY'S ANNUAL FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND INTERNAL CONTROL OVER FINANCIAL REPORTING, QUARTERLY

